Package crm.oilwhere.dto

package crm.oilwhere.dto
This package contains the controllers for the OilWhere CRM application.

DTOs are used to transfer data between different layers of the application. They ensure that only the required data is exposed or transferred, providing a clean separation between the domain and presentation layers.
